Package aom.scripting.xs.ai

Class GodPower

Object
GodPower
public class GodPower
extends Object
This class provides a collection of AI commands concerning God Powers.
Author:
Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com
Note
The power constants listed here are usually not required, what you really need is the respective techID.
